CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in New Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, March 4, 1967, pg. 12 reads: "Kingpins Of Section II - Giving rapt attention to Coach Bruce Weston (extreme right) starting members of the South Hills High School Tigers made ready for practice at the Civic Arena, Tuesday, in preparation for its test against Schenley High. From left (kneeling) Larry Anderson, Paul Litz, game Captain Alvin Rue, Paul Leonard.  Standing is Warren Parroll."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of South Hills High School Tigers basketball players, left to right: Larry Anderson, Paul Litz, Warren Parroll, standing; Alvin Rue, and Paul Leonard, listening to Coach Bruce Weston
